This dataset contains strikes done by action initiators like political parties, rebellion group, student unions, local communities, transport unions,ethnic and allinance group, struggle communities etc. It contains data from 2008 to 2013 AD. which was sourced from  United Nations Department of Safety and Security (UNDSS), Nepal Office by Nepal Rastra Bank.
